+-----------------------------+     +-----------------------------+
|                             |     |                             |
|  Blockchain Network 1       |     |  Blockchain Network 2       |
|  (e.g., Ethereum)           |     |  (e.g., Bitcoin)            |
|                             |     |                             |
+-----------------------------+     +-----------------------------+
            |                               |
            v                               v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                               |
|  Distributed Coin/Token Detection System                      |
|  - Nodes deployed on multiple networks                        |
|  - Detects new coins/tokens                                   |
|  - Gathers coin addresses                                     |
|    (e.g., 0xA1B2C3D4E5F6...)                                  |
|                                                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
            |                               |
            v                               v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                               |
|  Docker (Distributed Virtual Waiting Room)                    |
|  - Secures detected coins/tokens                              |
|  - Queues for mining                                          |
|  - Uses encryption and access controls                        |
|                                                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
            |                               |
            v                               v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                               |
|  Distributed Mining Network                                   |
|  - Miners validate and process coins/tokens                   |
|  - Employ consensus (e.g., Proof of Stake)                    |
|  - Generate unique identifiers                                |
|    (e.g., Coin ID: 123ABC, Reward ID: 789XYZ)                 |
|                                                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
            |                               |
            v                               v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                               |
|  CDI Blockchain Integration                                   |
|  - Adds validated coins/tokens                                |
|  - Ensures transparency and traceability                      |
|                                                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
            |                               |
            v                               v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                               |
|  Miner Rewards Distribution                                   |
|  - CDI coins issued as rewards                                |
|  - Sent to miner addresses                                    |
|    (e.g., 1F2E3D4C5B6A...)                                    |
|                                                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
